## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Frontend
        Pages --> Components
        Components --> Hooks
        Hooks --> API
        API --> Models_FE[Models]
    end
    
    subgraph Backend
        Router --> Service
        Service --> Databridge
        Databridge --> Database[(Database)]
        Service --> Proxy[External APIs]
    end
    
    API --> Router
```

### The Cardinal Rule
> **Lower layers NEVER import from higher layers.**

This creates a clean dependency flow and prevents circular imports.

