## Pre-Commit Checklist

### Backend
- [ ] All imports at top of file
- [ ] Models use Pydantic BaseModel with type hints (NO DICTIONARIES)
- [ ] Databridge only does data access (no business logic)
- [ ] Service contains business logic only
- [ ] Router has NO business logic
- [ ] No raw SQL in application code
- [ ] Tests written and passing
- [ ] No hardcoded configuration values

### Frontend
- [ ] Import order: External → Internal → Relative → Styles
- [ ] Named exports only (NO `export default`)
- [ ] Interfaces use PascalCase
- [ ] Hooks manage state and call APIs
- [ ] Components are pure UI (no API calls, no business logic)
- [ ] CSS Modules for styling (no inline styles)
- [ ] Tests written and passing

